            <listWit>
               
               <witness corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BLorient686">BL Or. 686 = BLW 257: 43 (1755-69): ff. 164ra-168va (f. 164r: 17 Maggābit); BLW "Theocritus the reader, ቴዎቅሪጦስ፡ አናግኖስጢስ፡";</witness>
               <witness corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BLorient690">BL Or. 690 = BLW 254: 5 (XV s.) (II parte del ms. BL Or. 689): ff. 12rb-21ra (f. 12r: 17 Maggābit);</witness>
               <witness corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BNFet131">BNZ 131: 12 (XIII s.): ff. 114vb-129vb (f. 114v: 17 Maggābit); BNZ "Martyre de Théostéricte, le lecteur (de Rome). ስምዕ፡ ዘቴዎቅሪጦስ፡ አናግኖስጢስ፡ ዘከመ፡ ተከለለ፡ ስምዐ፡ በእንተ፡ ክርስቶስ። Commencement: ተገብረ፡ መሥዋዕተ፡ ጽንሓሕ፡ እምኀቤሆሙ፡ ለመጣዕዋን፡ በቃጳጦሊያ፡ ወሮሜ። ወበው[እ]ቱ፡ መዋዕል፡ በከመ፡ ይትሐዘብ፡ እሙንቱ፡ ውፁኣን፡ እምእግዚኣብሔር፡ ፍሥሓ፡ ዐቢየ፡ ቦሙ፤ ወአሐቲ፡ እምኔሆን፡ ዕለት፡ ምክርት፡ ወጠባብት፡ ወመሥግላን፡ ወማረይት። …";</witness>
               <witness corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BNFabb179">BNA 179: 12 = BNAC 179: 13 = BNACR 163: 13 (1509): ff. 49va-55rc (f. 49va: 17 Maggābit);</witness>
               <witness corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/EMML1826"> EMML 1826: 8 (XIV-XV s.): ff. 65rb-75ra (f. 65r: 17 Maggābit); EMML "Martyrdom of Theocritus the Lector [Tēwoqriṭos anāgwenesṭis]. (17th of Maggābit). Conti Rossini (Manoscritti), p. 620; and Chaîne (D’Abbadie), no. 179, 13, p. 168. ስምዕ፡ ዘቴዎቅሪጦስ፡ አናጕንስጢስ፡ ዘከመ፡ ተከለለ፡ ስምዕ፡ በእንተ፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ። ወተገብረ፡ መሥዋዕተ፡ ጽንሐሕ፡ እምኀቤሆሙ፡ ለመጣዕያዊያን፡ በቀሚጦልያ፡ ወሮሜ፡ …";</witness>
               <witness corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/EMML2514">EMML 2514: 32 (1382-88): ff. 151ra-157rb (f. 151r: 17 Maggābit); EMML "Martyrdom of Theocritus the Lector. For 17 Maggābit. EMML 1826 (8). ስምዕ፡ ዘቴዎቅሪጦስ፡ አናጕንስጢስ፡ … ተገብረ፡ ጽንሓሐ፡ መሥዋዕት፡ እምኀቤሆሙ፡ ለመጣዕዋን፡ …";</witness>
               <witness corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/EMML6834">EMML 6834: 8 (XIV s.): ff. 51ra-60r (f. 51r: 17 Maggābit);</witness>
               <witness corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/EMML6951"> EMML 6951: 34 (XV s.): ff. 166ra-172rb (f. 166r: 17 Maggābit);</witness>
               <witness corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/Tanasee122">Ṭānāsee 122 = Dāgā Esṭifānos 11: 8 (XV s.): III: 4: ff. 32ra-39vb (f. 32r: 17 Maggābit).</witness>
               
            </listWit>
